Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.70,0:00:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，妳在叫什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我這封信的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.21,0:00:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎樣的人啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳覺得\N我應該怎麼稱呼對方才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.25,0:00:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文章跟字體都蠻堅毅的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是一位男性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.62,0:00:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜妳覺得呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得援助的條件是妳每週\N都要寫信給對方對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.49,0:00:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳應該自己想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小氣～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜每次都這麼冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我戳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹…幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳做什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現妮娜的弱點了～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.42,0:00:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我戳戳…\N住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到妮娜的笑臉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.03,0:01:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天妳幹得挺不賴的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.56,0:01:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心悸動無法平息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:02:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿盈內心 開始散放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何會如此不安呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法控制的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人不禁落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朝一日一定會抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算中途受挫也不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能踏出小小的一步 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嶄新的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第6話妮娜，被捲了…orz\N妳要是受夠教訓就別再得寸進尺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:03:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣\N也不能老是被妳壓著打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們兩個快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞鬥應該是優雅而美麗的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.02,0:03:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為乙HiME\N不可以任意衝動行事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問找我有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最近並沒有做出\N會被點名的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事情請妳務必幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責房間？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我跟妮娜一起\N負責奈緒學姊的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍珠第四名的奈緒學姊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想問我該做些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打掃房間啦，準備便當啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單來說就是照料生活起居
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相對的學姊會陪妳練習
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會指導妳的學業
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後然後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要服從姊姊的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算她對妳這樣或那樣\N也不可以違抗喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想老師是想要妳\N跟妮娜好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該吧，今天鬥得尤其激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，是因為我得寸進尺的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現妮娜的弱點了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱點？這很有意思喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依琳娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好性感喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮妮妮妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞～里～香～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有點意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個妮娜居然這麼怕癢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛唷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，有沒有聽說\N妮娜和愛莉卡還怕些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也，妳知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不清楚…關於…妮娜的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有有，愛莉卡是旱鴨子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天有游泳課
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒游泳過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我好期待唷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是她說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·王七個捲捲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡·夢宮三個捲捲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳們犯下忤逆我\N這個崇高的卡迪亞貴族之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判妳們螺旋捲捲之刑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色捲捲藍色捲捲黃色捲捲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色捲捲藍色捲捲黃色捲捲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.67,0:06:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捲啊捲啊被捲被捲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捲捲捲…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩渦啊，漩渦啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在這裡游泳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的浴缸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有覺悟了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想說“當然”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好像有個怪人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫做怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是聽說妳不會游泳\N特地跑來看戲的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是沒有游過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還不是不會游
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是會游
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才想問妳\N那件奇怪的泳裝是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:06:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳又說奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我們王家家傳\N具有悠久傳統的泳裝耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪就是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛，妳這個小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情真好呢\N真白女王跟愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會吵到別人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼各位請排好隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡同學，妳的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先練習將臉泡在水裡\N然後睜開眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那請加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等等會再過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不過就像是洗臉嘛，簡單啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真是讓人百看不厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡竟然會變成那樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個都只是呆而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃，好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，不可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都是女生耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，如果是妮娜的話，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位，請上岸來排隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著測驗每個人的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜那傢伙挺有兩下子的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚐嚐苦果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捲捲捲…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捲捲捲…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是妳有個萬一，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:10:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫子老師她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急急忙忙聯絡王少校來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼會溺水呢？真不像妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好向埃爾斯汀同學\N和螞蟻道謝喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她們救了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妳們？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然跳下去了\N但是卻跟妳一起溺水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過多虧這樣我讓臉泡到水了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是埃爾斯汀同學\N熟練地幫妳做了人工呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人工…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思給妳添麻煩了\N埃爾斯汀同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會是麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮依娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，妮娜，妳幹了什麼蠢事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位不是王少校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到處女的花園
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渾身帶刺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是有得到你們期望的成績喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然各位特地跑來，但是很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得讓妮娜同學再休息一會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒學姊認識那個王少校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妮娜一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是靠阿爾泰的稅金來這裡唸書的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在阿爾泰物色可以成為\N乙HiME的少女然後扔到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾泰是個寒冷又貧窮的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大公凪尚未擁有乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們根本就是相中這點\N想增強軍事力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍事力…是想打仗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.92,0:12:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管增加多少軍隊或戰車戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全比不上一個Meister啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME的強度\N就代表國家的軍事力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以待遇一直很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳到底為什麼想當乙HiME ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮很帥又很強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這點倒是跟妮娜很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也是既單純又笨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該很沮喪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她覺得“讓父親丟臉了”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是孤兒的妮娜被他收養了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就為了那個爛男人拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是個大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜真的很努力耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也不用一直罵她笨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆也說過\N罵別人笨蛋的人才是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳果然很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:14:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜的話不用管她也沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說，不要管她比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她又笨又好強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·王妳嚐到苦頭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒捲夠這個愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下就是湮滅證據
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳池現在是禁止進入的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆·尤伊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想以三和弦的身份\N調查一下意外的起因而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份心意很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是校方的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在釐清原因之前\N我不會讓任何人進來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依琳娜，這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是\N沒有移殖到這個星球上的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是想問
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個游泳池裡真的有東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不敢肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妮娜是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我出那種洋相的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜好像被什麼附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝膠安基爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個星球上原有的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,型態類似地球上的鰻魚和水母
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體組織的98％是水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:15:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在水中無法以肉眼辨識
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡在高濃度的鹽水就會白濁化\N就比較容易用肉眼辨識了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為學園長批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次特別允許
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果沒用的話\N妳們也很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子鹽全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬來了搬來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能休息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓那傢伙\N在光天化日之下現形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快現形吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我一網打盡你們！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒東西耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:16:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:16:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然浪費食物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭要罰掃地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉亞女士\N剩下的事情交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好監督她們的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.95,0:17:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就請妳們好好打掃乾淨\N然後立刻離開游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點動手收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.23,0:17:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜挽回名譽的機會\N到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，黏答答的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黏答答？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，妳該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明就是從\N標示是鹽的地方拿來的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這個是砂糖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞～里～香～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給這種生物糖分的話\N單一個體會融合吸收周圍的水分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且巨大化？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依琳娜，快去找老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該…該怎麼辦啊，妮娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能穿舞鬥服的話，這種對手…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩…詩帆姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，妳去當誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.74,0:19:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用這個再試一次看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了救那種人\N還這麼拼命才會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:19:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們果然是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解…解不開…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨～妳捲捲了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這模樣真不賴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩渦居然被捲了，成何體統嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱麗葉，妳快點救我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拜託別人的時候\N該說什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不過妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜\N這下子妳又欠我一個人情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，妳也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱麗葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳居然把我丟在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙子！壞人！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒說要安穩地救妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳耍什麼笨啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱麗葉～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會捲死妳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前略，叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定以“叔叔”稱呼叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒學姊告訴我\N這樣子叫會讓年長男性高興
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒學姊是我負責房間的姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說我很有趣，要收我當手下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這個學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有宿舍同寢的妮娜，埃爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及班上的同學們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來到學園之後交了很多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:21:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好醜的字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上課雖然很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.51,0:22:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是每天都很快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是叔叔的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.35,0:22:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔，謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣會實現願望 Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等著我的故事 現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其逃避 不如挺身面對更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是少女的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.73,0:22:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力唷\N就算內心突然感到寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.27,0:23:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以笑容面對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼NO NO NO 你的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有快樂的未來 我想守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.62,0:23:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄的心意 比寶石更耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.09,0:23:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.61,0:23:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一集到底是怎麼回事？\N（蒼之舞／少女的契約）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會這麼倒黴…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.68,0:23:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…果然是妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.35,0:23:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的交給妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.42,0:23:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.45,0:23:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.52,0:23:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,習慣之後\N妳遲早會覺得舒爽的




